Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 Rick\N{\fs38}Hey, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周末有个科技展览 我必须要交个手工作业\N{\fs38}I have to make a project for the science fair this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮我吗\N{\fs38}You think you could help me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便\N{\fs38}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 传统而言 科技展览应该是老爸和儿子的事\N{\fs38}Well, I mean, traditionally, science fairs are a father-son thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 科学而言 传统是傻瓜的事\N{\fs38}Well, scientifically, traditions are an idiot thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 我觉得你和你爸一起做科学作业应该挺有意思的\N{\fs38}Morty, I think it would be fun for you to work on a science project with your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.66,0:00:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 对啊 老爸\N{\fs38}Un... Yeah, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起做怎么样\N{\fs38}Why don't we do it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fs38}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儿子 找我就是找对人了\N{\fs38}You backed the right horse on this one, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把蜡笔翻出来 喝点咖啡\N{\fs38}We'll get out the crayons, brew some coffee,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两三天就能搞定\N{\fs38}and knock this thing out on two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我存在的意义是什么\N{\fs38}What is my purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把黄油拿来\N{\fs38}Pass the butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢\N{\fs38}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸 开车送我去上班\N{\fs38}Dad, I need a ride to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick可以送你\N{\fs38}Maybe Rick can give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要帮Morty搞科研\N{\fs38}I'm helping Morty with science.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事\N{\fs38}I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\fs38}Doing what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他事\N{\fs38}Uh, anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我存在的意义是什么\N{\fs38}What is my purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.76,0:00:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,递黄油\N{\fs38}You pass butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs38}Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.57,0:01:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到这个世界\N{\fs38}Yeah, welcome to the club, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啥时候找到工作的\N{\fs38}Since when do you have a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上个礼拜\N{\fs38}Since last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在二手古董店做兼职\N{\fs38}It's part-time at this little vintage thrift store.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老板很聪明 很古怪 但是他对我很好\N{\fs38}My boss is this really smart, eccentric old man that treats me nice and values me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦噢\N{\fs38}Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.01,0:01:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到是要见见是何方神圣\N{\fs38}Can't wait to meet this fascinating character.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万别\N{\fs38}Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.15,0:01:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs38}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.89,0:01:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿以前不是珍宝果汁店吗\N{\fs38}Well, when did this stop being Jamba Juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们刚刚开张\N{\fs38}I've just recently opened for business, mister, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Goldenfold先生\N{\fs38}Goldenfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我名字\N{\fs38}You know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是倍感亲切\N{\fs38}That's disarming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还知道你渴望能有美人相伴\N{\fs38}I also know you long for female company.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离婚后我一直很空虚\N{\fs38}You know, it has been lonely since the divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍宝果汁无法填补的空虚\N{\fs38}Some voids can't be filled with Jamba Juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这须后水能让女人为你神魂颠倒\N{\fs38}This aftershave makes a man quite irresistible to women.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要钱\N{\fs38}Free of charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的东西要的都不是钱\N{\fs38}One never pays here -- not with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道这么多久够了 谢了\N{\fs38}Nothing to read into there. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起所需先生 我迟到了\N{\fs38}Sorry I'm late, Mr.Needful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我外公 Rick\N{\fs38}This is my grandpa, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他马上就走\N{\fs38}He was just leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我 Rick 你渴望什么\N{\fs38}Tell me, Rick, what do you desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自给自足\N{\fs38}Eh, I make my own stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你是什么 魔鬼吗\N{\fs38}So, what are you -- like, the Devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 不好意思\N{\fs38}What? Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也说不准 突然冒出来个商店\N{\fs38}I don't know. Story comes out of nowhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖一些古怪的老玩意儿\N{\fs38}All the shit's old and creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是魔鬼吗 或者恶魔 矮妖\N{\fs38}Are you the Devil? A Demon? Leprechaun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick外公\N{\fs38}Grandpa Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没批评他 只是有话直说\N{\fs38}Hey, I'm not judging. Just like shoot straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我毕竟是搞科学的\N{\fs38}I'm a man of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 那你或许用得上这个\N{\fs38}Ah, then perhaps you could make use of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个显微镜能揭秘不可思议之物\N{\fs38}This microscope reveals things beyond comprehension.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公 回家喝你的酒\N{\fs38}Grandpa, go home and drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做个太阳系模型怎么样\N{\fs38}Why don't we do a model of the solar system?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我像你这么的时候 我老爹就和我做这个\N{\fs38}That's what my dad did with me when I was your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好啊\N{\fs38}Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然Rick成天待在他的实验室\N{\fs38}You know, Rick's in his lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞些电子人啊 虫洞啊 那些奇怪的东西\N{\fs38}making cyborgs and wormholes and all that weird stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这才是真正的科学\N{\fs38}but this is real science.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和儿子 一起造行星\N{\fs38}A man and his boy, making planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 用乒乓球做冥王星怎么样\N{\fs38}Hey, how about we use a Ping-Pong ball for Pluto?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后木星\N{\fs38}And then Jupiter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 冥王星好像不是行星\N{\fs38}Uh, actually, I don't think Pluto is a Planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儿子 冥王星当然是行星\N{\fs38}Of course Pluto is a planet, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我三年级就知道了\N{\fs38}I learned that in the third grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对 但是后来有人改了\N{\fs38}Well, yeah, but you know they changed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 行星这种事怎么会改呢\N{\fs38}Morty, nobody changed the planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚在谷歌上查了\N{\fs38}I just Googled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冥王星不是行星\N{\fs38}Pluto is not a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2006年就改了\N{\fs38}They changed it in 2006.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 这个我听说了\N{\fs38}Yeah, I heard about that, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不同意\N{\fs38}And I disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不同意\N{\fs38}You disagree?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同意\N{\fs38}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学中产生分歧很正常 Morty\N{\fs38}It's possible to disagree in science, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冥王星以前是行星\N{\fs38}Pluto was a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来被一些自以为是的狗屁委员会否定了\N{\fs38}Some committee of fancy assholes disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我否定回去 把乒乓球给我\N{\fs38}I disagree back. Give me a Ping-Pong ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs38}Um, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我要去\N{\fs38}I-I just have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找Rick 然后背着我说冥王星的事吗\N{\fs38}Go find Rick and go over my head about Pluto?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我只是要去厕所 神经\N{\fs38}No. Geez, I just got to go the bathroom. Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 很好\N{\fs38}Oh. Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定会很好玩的\N{\fs38}This is gonna be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 让我 让我 \N{\fs38}Hey, Morty, let me let me let me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问你个问题\N{\fs38}ask you a question real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上有邪力吗 如果有\N{\fs38}Does Evil exist, and if so,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有办法检测和测量吗\N{\fs38}can one detect and measure it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃\N{\fs38}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个设问句 Morty\N{\fs38}Rhetorical question, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是"有并且可以 只要你是天才"\N{\fs38}The answer's "yes, you just have to be a genius."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真赞\N{\fs38}Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你姐的老板给了我这个显微镜\N{\fs38}Your sister's boss give me a microscope
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西会使让我变成弱智\N{\fs38}that would have made me retarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 噢 天啊 Rick\N{\fs38}Ooh. Oh, boy, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你不该用这个词\N{\fs38}I'm don't think you're allowed to say that word, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 我没有对残障人士不敬的意思\N{\fs38}Morty, I'm not disparaging the differently abled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在陈述事实 如果我用了这显微镜\N{\fs38}I'm stating the fact that if I had used this microscope,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西就会使我的智商降低\N{\fs38}it would have made me mentally retarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}That's retarded(真逊 真差劲)\N常因为暗含对残障人士的不尊重而被认为是"政治不正确"的话\Nretard一词本指先天残障 后引申出"糟糕 愚蠢"之意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 我说的不是逻辑问题\N{\fs38}Okay, yeah, but I don't think it's about logic, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这个词已经变成了某些自己以为是的政治集团\N{\fs38}I think the word has just become a symbolic issue for powerful groups
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿来说事儿的东西了\N{\fs38}that feel like they're doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真扯淡\N{\fs38}That's retarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在说什么\N{\fs38}What are you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然 啥都没说\N{\fs38}Apparently, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问他冥王星是不是行星了对吧\N{\fs38}You asked him if Pluto is planet, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 没有  - 不是\N{\fs38}- No! - It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 Rick\N{\fs38}Shut up, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇啊\N{\fs38}Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管别人说什么\N{\fs38}I don't care what anyone says.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果它以前可以是行星 那现在也可以\N{\fs38}If it can be a planet, it can be a planet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行星 行星 行星 行星\N{\fs38}Planet, planet, planet, planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学一点吧 Jerry\N{\fs38}Stay scientific, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这瓶须后水的确让女人为我倾倒\N{\fs38}This aftershave made women want me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它也让我阳痿了\N{\fs38}but it also made me impotent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做任何事都要付出代价的 Goldenfold先生\N{\fs38}A price for everything, Mr. Goldenfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何事情都有代价\N{\fs38}A price for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝啊\N{\fs38}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会没想到\N{\fs38}How could I not see this coming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的欲望 我的贪婪\N{\fs38}My lust! My greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我活该\N{\fs38}I deserved this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种血清可以中和副作用\N{\fs38}This serum should counteract the negative effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fs38}Holy cats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑娘们 我们走吧\N{\fs38}Ladies, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么教训都没接受\N{\fs38}I haven't learned a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以拿回去了\N{\fs38}Here. You can have this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有用吗\N{\fs38}You didn't use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然用了 用来开发了这个\N{\fs38}Sure I did, to develop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}Twilgiht Zone 1959年电视剧 并在1983年拍摄电影\NRay Bradbury 美国奇幻恐怖小说作家\NFriday the 13th: The Series 电视剧 其中主角姐弟俩继承了一家有各种被诅咒物品的古董店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它能探测并分类你这些"阴阳魔界" "Ray Bradbury" \N{\fs38}It detects and catalogs all your "twilight zone," Ray Bradbury,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"十三号星期五" 巫毒破烂玩意儿\N{\fs38}"friday the 13th:the series" voodoo crap magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你说不定会想要\N{\fs38}I thought you might want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免得你不小心卖给谁 比如\N{\fs38}so you didn't accidentally sell anybody, say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能创作出最畅销谋杀案\N{\fs38}A typewriter that generates best-selling murder mysteries
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并让它们真实发生的打字机\N{\fs38}and then makes the murders happen in real life? Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静点\N{\fs38}Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想确保顾客都知道他们买了什么吗\N{\fs38}Don't you want to make sure people know what they're getting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会是故意的吧 卖这种\N{\fs38}You're not intentionally selling...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让丑女人变美但会让她们失明的美容霜\N{\fs38}Beauty cream that makes ugly ladies pretty but also makes them blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是荒谬之极\N{\fs38}I find this all quite preposterous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我说 好先生 哦 哼哼 哦 哦\N{\fs38}Oh, I say, good Sir. Oh, harrumph. Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮\N{\fs38}That's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道三小时后就变成它穿着你了吗\N{\fs38}You know it's gonna be wearing you in three hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想让我报警吗\N{\fs38}Do I need to call the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去 你可以用我的电话\N{\fs38}Here, you can use my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\fs38}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不会让你失聪的 我又不是黑心商\N{\fs38}It won't make you deaf because I'm not a hack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 别这样\N{\fs38}Hey, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你以为自己多[哔]棒 你[哔]蠢蛋  - 住手\N{\fs38}- You think you're [Bleep] so great, you stupid piece of [Bleep] shit.  - Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 住手 嘿 嘿  - 你丫[哔]\N{\fs38}- Stop! Hey! Hey!  - [Bleep] you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻住手\N{\fs38}Stop it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick爷爷 我喜欢在这工作\N{\fs38}Grandpa Rick, I like working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在为魔鬼工作\N{\fs38}You work for the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么样\N{\fs38}So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说怎么样\N{\fs38}So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 就算他是魔鬼又怎样 Rick\N{\fs38}Yes, so what if he's the devil, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少魔鬼有份工作\N{\fs38}At least the devil has a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少他在社区很活跃\N{\fs38}At least he's active in the community.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么了\N{\fs38}What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃我们的 然后做些小玩意\N{\fs38}You eat our food and make gadgets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走好不送\N{\fs38}Buh-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎哟\N{\fs38}Wh...oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉 所需先生\N{\fs38}I'm sorry, Mr. Needful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会清理干净的\N{\fs38}I'll clean that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道怎么处理从里面跑出来的女鬼 但是\N{\fs38}I don't know what I can do about the ghost lady that came out of it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fs38}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:06:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 你爷爷说的没错\N{\fs38}Summer, you know, your grandfather's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:06:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家商店诅咒人们 \N{\fs38}This store curses people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的生意\N{\fs38}That's my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs38}Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快餐让人们患上糖尿病 \N{\fs38}Fast-food gives people diabetes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服装店都有血汗工厂\N{\fs38}and clothing stores have sweatshops.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雇佣青少年的公司有哪家不邪恶的吗\N{\fs38}Is there a company hiring teenagers that isn't evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的第一份工作\N{\fs38}This is my first job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我很好 所需先生 \N{\fs38}You've been nice to me, Mr. Needful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你尊重我\N{\fs38}You respect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 叫我"魔鬼"\N{\fs38}Please, call me "the devil".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 还是算了吧  - 说得对 上班时间还是算了\N{\fs38}- I'd rather not, actually.  - Yes, perhaps not during business hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了 我要填写冥王星是行星的声明\N{\fs38}I told you, I want to file a declaration that Pluto is a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我儿子的科学课就要挂科了 \N{\fs38}Well, then my son's going to fail his science class,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那样的话 \N{\fs38}and when that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一个起诉的就是你们\N{\fs38}I'm suing you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我算明白NASA里的"A"是什么意思了\N{\fs38}I think I know what the "A" in NASA stands for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 你这游戏最后打算怎么办\N{\fs38}Dad, what's your endgame?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是游戏 傻瓜\N{\fs38}Ain't no game, sucka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就做一个八颗行星的太阳系不好吗\N{\fs38}Why don't we just make the solar system with eight planets?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是还简单些吗\N{\fs38}It's even easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 那我们为什么不直接把伽利略烧死在刑柱上\N{\fs38}Sure, sure, and why don't we just burn Galileo at the stake
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他说太阳是圆的\N{\fs38}for saying the sun is round?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学并不总是那么简单的 Morty\N{\fs38}Science isn't always easy, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 哇 搞什么鬼\N{\fs38}Whoa! Whoa! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是小疯疯国王 冥王星的统治者\N{\fs38}I'm King Flippy Nips, ruler of Pluto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在例行监视你们星球的时候偶然发现了你\N{\fs38}We discovered you quite by accident during routine surveillance of your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是给了航空航天局的人点颜色啊\N{\fs38}You really gave it to those guys at NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是 你懂的 有时候科学有关信念\N{\fs38}I was...you know, sometimes science is about conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要向你们介绍一些非常赞同你们的人\N{\fs38}I'd like to introduce you to a few people that very much agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我\N{\fs38}Oh, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冥王星的子民们\N{\fs38}Plutonians.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry Smith是地球来的科学家 \N{\fs38}Jerry Smith is a scientist from earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正在创造一个太阳系的模型\N{\fs38}where he's creating a model of our solar system.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 向冥王星宣布你的决定\N{\fs38}Jerry, tell Pluto about your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 冥王星是个行星\N{\fs38}Um...Pluto's a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冥王星是个[哔]行星 贱人\N{\fs38}Pluto's a [beep] planet, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fs38}Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的脑子绝对会被冲昏\N{\fs38}This is definitely gonna go to his head.
